                    <note type="project" target="#rel01">A line has been drawn in ink through
                        this autograph request. Whitman pasted this letter to a November 11, 1876,
                        autograph request from W. A Stagg that has been cut into two pieces. He
                        has pasted half of Stagg's letter to the bottom of Barton's note and 
                        the other half of Stagg's letter to the top.</note>
                    <note type="project" target="#rel02">Whitman then used the backs of all of these letters to compose a draft
